Kenney Bui: The Life And Death Of A High School Football Player Kenny Bui was the first high school football player to die in a month. The Guardian By Les Carpenter Posted: 10/14/2015 11:20 AM EDT 
In the back of a funeral home on Seattleâ€™s south end, a Vietnamese immigrant father mourns the boy who loved football, the Seahawks, and a defensive backfield called the Legion of Boom.
